<p dir="auto">Enqueuer is a platform that provides the following capabilities:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Support for multi protocols<br></li>
<li>Chainable message flows <br></li>
<li>Friendly for developers and non developers <br></li>
<li>Easily extensible through third party <a href="http://github.com/enqueuer-land/plugins-list">plugins</a>, including <a href="https://github.com/enqueuer-land/plugin-scaffold">yours</a> <br></li>
<li>Automated end-to-end testing <br></li>
<li>Place tests front and center</li>
